name: Angel Di Maria
bio: Angel Di Maria is a talented chef with a passion for farm-to-table cooking. Born and raised in a small town in the Midwest, she grew up with a deep appreciation for fresh, local ingredients. After completing culinary school, Alice worked at a number of top restaurants before opening her own farm-to-table bistro. Her dishes are known for their vibrant flavors and beautiful presentation, showcasing the best ingredients that the season has to offer. Alice is also a vocal advocate for sustainable farming practices and is passionate about educating others on the importance of eating locally and seasonally.
